So that was a lot of
fun to do that analysis.

00:28:10.210 --> 00:28:14.280
Then I have a little bit on
game theory and strategy.

00:28:14.280 --> 00:28:18.510
My point there is
that by-- like birds

00:28:18.510 --> 00:28:21.110
are able to evolve to
have particular strategies

00:28:21.110 --> 00:28:25.280
and managers are also
able to evolve and have

00:28:25.280 --> 00:28:28.610
optimal strategies, possibly
not by being the smartest people

00:28:28.610 --> 00:28:31.890
but just by watching each other
and adopting their strategies.

00:28:31.890 --> 00:28:34.440
And I talk about why you should
have three points for a win,

00:28:34.440 --> 00:28:36.148
because it makes more
attacking football.

