between people

00:28:56.280 --> 00:28:58.550
and it's really to do
with exponential growth

00:28:58.550 --> 00:29:01.510
and infection.

00:29:01.510 --> 00:29:03.510
Then I have a bit on
collective wisdom.

00:29:03.510 --> 00:29:08.390
So how betting provides some
form of collective wisdom.

00:29:08.390 --> 00:29:12.900
There was this lovely book,
"This Wisdom of Crowds,"

00:29:12.900 --> 00:29:14.510
and so I look a
bit deeper at some

00:29:14.510 --> 00:29:17.180
of the assumptions in "This
Wisdom of Crowds" in that.

