00:45:12.436 --> 00:45:14.210
So tournaments
like the FA Cup are

00:45:14.210 --> 00:45:17.570
known for being very surprising
and having a lot of shocks.

00:45:17.570 --> 00:45:20.984
How much of that do you think
is because premiership teams

00:45:20.984 --> 00:45:22.400
are playing lower
league teams who

00:45:22.400 --> 00:45:25.920
have like incompatible networks
that they don't see often.

00:45:25.920 --> 00:45:29.190
Or how much of it is just
due to some kind of magic

00:45:29.190 --> 00:45:32.250
that you'll never be able
to statistically predict?

00:45:32.250 --> 00:45:33.650
DAVID SUMPTER: Yeah.

00:45:33.650 --> 00:45:36.000
Some of it is going to be
down to that sort of thing.

00:45:36.000 --> 00:45:38.130
But the thing you have
to start off remembering

00:45:38.130 --> 00:45:40.490
is that 2/3 of
everything that happens

00:45:40.490 --> 00:45:43.740
in a football match is
random in the outcome and 1/3

00:45:43.740 --> 00:45:44.604
is down to skill.

00:45:44.604 --> 00:45:46.020
And you can think
of it like this.

00:45:46.020 --> 00:45:47.980
So you have three goals
in the football match.

00:45:47.980 --> 00:45:51.170
One of them goes to the best
team and then two of them

00:45:51.170 --> 00:45:53.460
are spread randomly
between the two teams.

00:45:53.460 --> 00:45:55.910
And it's maybe it's
a bit more than one

00:45:55.910 --> 00:45:58.100
maybe in an FA Cup
match, but there's always

00:45:58.100 --> 00:45:59.990
that sort of random
chance that the teams are

00:45:59.990 --> 00:46:00.980
going to go through.

00:46:00.980 --> 00:46:04.150
So you're always going to have
one of those dream stories,

00:46:04.150 --> 00:46:06.800
you know, the giant
killers or whatever.

00:46:06.800 --> 00:46:09.120
And probably the
first thing to look at

00:46:09.120 --> 00:46:10.870
is the random
explanation before you

00:46:10.870 --> 00:46:14.140
start to look at any tactical
genius of these division

00:46:14.140 --> 00:46:18.070
two trainers who have got
them up to that level.

00:46:18.070 --> 00:46:19.934
But that's why you
want to have cups

00:46:19.934 --> 00:46:21.600
and you don't just
want to have leagues.

00:46:21.600 --> 00:46:23.570
But apart from this
season, leagues

00:46:23.570 --> 00:46:26.190
have been extremely
predictable and cups always

00:46:26.190 --> 00:46:28.310
throw up a bit
more of excitement

00:46:28.310 --> 00:46:31.030
